headline: State Street Investment Management Expands Actively Managed Target Maturity ETFs Suite
summary: BOSTON, September 17, 2025--State Street Investment Management announced today the launch of the SPDR速 SSGA My2035 Corporate Bond ETF (MYCO) and SPDR速 SSGA My2031 Municipal Bond ETF (MYMK). The two funds expand the SPDR MyIncome ETF Suite, which debuted in 2024 as one of the first actively managed corporate and municipal target maturity bond ETFs in the U.S. market.

headline: State Street Elects Brian Porter to its Board of Directors
summary: BOSTON, September 17, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) today announced the election of Brian Porter to its Board of Directors.

headline: Is State Street Stock Outperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Over the past year, State Street has delivered stronger returns than the Nasdaq Composite, and analysts remain guardedly positive about its future performance.
